## 🎬 Core Use Cases

### Use Case 1: Vehicle Entry (Happy Path)
1. Vehicle arrives at entry gate
2. System checks capacity
3. System finds available spot using AllocationStrategy
4. System assigns spot, issues ticket
5. Vehicle parks at assigned spot

### Use Case 2: Vehicle Exit
1. Vehicle returns to exit gate
2. Driver scans ticket
3. System calculates fee using PricingStrategy
4. Driver pays
5. System frees spot, vehicle exits

### Use Case 3: Lot Full
1. Vehicle arrives
2. System checks capacity → No spot available
3. System rejects entry
4. Display "LOT FULL"

### Use Case 4: Ticket Lost
1. Driver at exit without ticket
2. System uses license plate to find entry (optional)
3. OR charge maximum daily rate
4. Process payment, exit

