## ⚠️ Common Interview Mistakes

| Mistake | Better Approach |
|---------|-----------------|
| No size matching | Spot must fit vehicle size |
| Price on Spot | Price based on vehicle type + duration |
| No ticket | Need ticket to track entry time |
| No strategy pattern | Use Strategy for pricing + allocation |
| Single floor only | Design for multiple floors |

